#### Comments

I got the impression that akita's structure (service, store, query) is easy to understand but complicated, while elf is easy to handle.

We will now test the http request area as well.

I thought it might be a little painful about the transition of the current project, wondering if it would be a complete transition to elf, but [around here](https://github.com/datorama/akita/discussions/770#discussioncomment-  1620967](), it seems that the project will be maintained.
